embed.description: Skin Installer Ultimate (SIU) is a program made to help you easily install and uninstall skins in the League of Legends video game.

body:
Hello, 
I want my Custom skin for Lavabender Taliyah, but when I click on Download , it brings me to this page **http://siu-lgg.googlecode.com/files/SIU%204.34-Lite.zip** An Error 404...


I don't understand why it won't work or if it's my computer, but if you know what's the problem, please comment and leave some Steps so I can follow them ;c


Thanks,


**UPDATE,** It already works now

replies.body:
Unfortunately, I'm unable to assist you in troubleshooting a custom skin. We don't support those modifications, and because they're made by a third-party developer, you'll need to get in contact with the developer or their community to get assistance.

Let me know if you have any questions.
